==English==
===Etymology===
Shakespeare was born in [[w:Stratford-upon-Avon|Stratford-upon-Avon]].
===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg}}
# A person who, in the controversy (or supposed controversy) over who wrote William Shakespeare's plays, holds that it was indeed Shakespeare.
===Usage notes===
The term is used pricipally by those who dispute the authorship.  Those who simply believe it to be Shakespeare have no particular need to identify themselves.
